The paper discusses deep neural networks and their vulnerability to adversarial attacks, which are common topics in the sub-fields of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and cybersecurity (cs.CR). The paper also proposes a new method for improving the robustness of these networks, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE).
